Feature: Vision

TodoApp allows the user to keep track of their todos.

Goals

* Enable users to keep track of what they need to do
* Improve users' organisation


Capabilities

* See all todos in one place
* Add items to the list: Items have a label
* Add a description of items: adds a description field to each item. Double click items so see the field.
* Mark items as done
* Filter through items: adds filter functionality: show all, show done, show not done
* Search items: adds a search field (searches all the labels).
